reviewText: This is not like an original recording.  The quality is weak and the acts are divided up with gaps almost like it's not a complete show.
It's great to have this video showcasing LGBT community members, and a great introduction to some comedians you might not know.
Was in great shape & I loved the dvd. Hilarious & with  off-stage commentaries from most of the comedians. Even a section for a website with more LGBT films. Well done!
